thread.title: Jill
thread.title_full: TAXIBOX mobile self-storage reviewed by Jill

author: Jill
title: Jill
text: They brought us the taxi boxes, we filled them to the brim with stuff we wanted to keep but not have cluttering our house while it was on the market. We attached our own locks and Taxi Box came and collected the boxes on a specified day. You have access to your stuff while it's in storage, if they're given a day's notice. Otherwise, you let them know when and where you want the boxes delivered, they bring them to your door, give you time to empty them and then take them away!
